snippet.title: Lonely Mountains: Downhill - Greenlight Trailer [Pre Alpha]
snippet.description:
The project will soon be on Kickstarter! Sign up for our newsletter and unlock exclusive rewards before the campaign starts:
http://lonelymountains.com/kickstarter

Thanks so much for your support! We passed greenlight in only 4 days & received awesome and super motiviating feedback during the last months!
